name: Ps2-linux-website
tagline: This is the website that hosts programs and documentation for the PlayStation 2 system and Linux distributions
body:
### Welcome To Darren Raineys PS2 Linux Support Website

### Documentation
Information about the system and programming guides can be found at https://darrenrainey.github.io/ps2linux/docs

### Guides
Help and guides can be found at https://darrenrainey.github.io/ps2linux/guides this contains reliable/tested methods and guides for PlayStation 2 Linux

### Authors and Contributors
Page Created On 19/06/2016 by @DarrenRainey

### Support or Contact
If you have any questions or problems open an issue on https://github.com/DarrenRainey/PS2-Linux-Website
